Working at SCI: Benefits and Career DevelopmentEvery day, we are reminded of how precious life is. Our business understands that each employee has a unique perspective and exceptional qualities as a caregiver and member of the community. We celebrate what is unique in each of us and we look for employees who believe that you can't get something out of your career if you don't put something into it.
We put strong focus on developing careers and skills. That's why we offer our employees continued learning and development, competitive benefits, performance incentives, and unique opportunities to share.
At SCI, we'll change everything you ever thought about working in the funeral and cemetery business.












